904static uint16_T look1_iu16lu64n48_binlcse(uint16_T u0, const uint16_T bp0[],



905  const uint16_T table[], uint32_T maxIndex)



906{



907  uint16_T y;



908  uint64_T frac;



909  uint32_T iRght;



910  uint32_T iLeft;



911  uint32_T bpIdx;



912



913  /* Lookup 1-D



914     Search method: 'binary'



915     Use previous index: 'off'



916     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



917     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



918     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



919     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



920     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



921   */



922  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



923     Index Search method: 'binary'



924     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



925     Use previous index: 'off'



926     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



927     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



928     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



929   */



930  if (u0 <= bp0[0U]) {



931    iLeft = 0U;



932    frac = 0ULL;



933  } else if (u0 < bp0[maxIndex]) {



934    /* Binary Search */



935    bpIdx = maxIndex >> 1U;



936    iLeft = 0U;



937    iRght = maxIndex;



938    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



939      if (u0 < bp0[bpIdx]) {



940        iRght = bpIdx;



941      } else {



942        iLeft = bpIdx;



943      }



944



945      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



946    }



947



948    frac = ((uint64_T)(uint16_T)((uint32_T)u0 - bp0[iLeft]) << 48) / (uint16_T)



949      ((uint32_T)bp0[iLeft + 1U] - bp0[iLeft]);



950  } else {



951    iLeft = maxIndex - 1U;



952    frac = 281474976710656ULL;



953  }



954



955  /* Interpolation 1-D



956     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



957     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



958     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



959     Overflow mode: 'wrapping'



960   */



961  if (table[iLeft + 1U] >= table[iLeft]) {



962    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)(uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft + 1U]



963      - table[iLeft]) * frac) >> 48) + table[iLeft]);



964  } else {



965    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft] - (uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)



966      table[iLeft] - table[iLeft + 1U]) * frac) >> 48));



967  }



968



969  return y;



970}

1414static void NEUTRAL_STATE(void)



1415{

1424      }

1426    break;

1428   case IN_NO_NEUTRAL:

1431    }



1432    break;

1436    {



1437      rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE = IN_NEUTRAL;



1438    }



1439    break;



1440



1441   case IN_UNSET_NEUTRAL:



1442    if ((rtDW.is_GEARSHIFT == IN_DOWN_END) || (rtDW.is_GEARSHIFT == IN_UP_END))

1445    }



1446    break;



1447  }

1450/* Function for Chart: '<S5>/GCULogic' */



1451static int32_T Gearshift_getTime(void)



1452{



1453  int32_T time;



1454  if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_START) {



1455    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



1456      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DEFAULT_NT_CLUTCH_DELAY];



1457    } else {



1458      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DELAY];



1459    }



1460  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_PUSH) {



1461    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



1462      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_CLUTCH_DELAY];



1463    } else {



1464      switch (rtDW.RateTransition36[6]) {



1465       case 1:



1466        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_1_2];



1467        break;



1468



1469       case 2:



1470        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_2_3];



1471        break;



1472



1473       case 3:



1474        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_3_4];



1475        break;



1476



1477       case 4:



1478        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_4_5];



1479        break;



1480



1481       default:



1482        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_2_3];



1483        break;



1484      }



1485    }



1486  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_REBOUND) {



1487    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



1488      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_REBOUND_1_N];



1489    } else {



1490      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_REBOUND];



1491    }



1492  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_BRAKE) {



1493    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



1494      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_BRAKE_1_N];



1495    } else {



1496      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_BRAKE];



1497    }



1498  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_START) {



1499    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)CLUTCH];



1500  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_PUSH) {



1501    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_PUSH];



1502  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_REBOUND) {



1503    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_REBOUND];



1504  } else {



1505    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_BRAKE];



1506  }



1507



1508  return time;



1509}
